comments.body:
Can remove the bottom `scriptChange = GetScriptForDestination(dest);` call if `GetReservedDestination` failed (no valid destination).
```c++
auto op_dest = reservedest.GetReservedDestination(true);
if (!op_dest) {
    error = _("Transaction needs a change address, but we can't generate it.") + Untranslated(" ") + op_dest.GetError();
} else {
    scriptChange = GetScriptForDestination(op_dest.GetObj());
}
```

